title: BREAKING: Malmo rocked by EXPLOSION as Swedish police deploy bomb squad to block of flats
text:
BREAKING: Malmo rocked by EXPLOSION as Swedish police deploy bomb squad to block of flats BREAKING: Malmo rocked by EXPLOSION as Swedish police deploy bomb squad to block of flats SWEDISH police have deployed the bomb squad and cornered off a block of flats in Malmo superb after a suspected grenade attack. PUBLISHED: 23:19,   23:37, Mon, Feb 27, 2017 TWITTERâ€¢EXPRESSEN Malmo has been rocked by a suspected grenade attack 
According to local reports a suspected hand grenade was detonated in Lindangen area of the city. 
Police have secured the area and one adult has been taken to hospital, Expressen reports. Shocking images depict violence in Sweden Tue, February 21, 2017
